Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.50,0:00:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.50,0:00:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.77,0:01:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多數異界體正從西南方接近
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.00,0:01:40.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計再三十分鐘抵達
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.81,0:01:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是群體行動的類型
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.57,0:01:44.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要打倒帶頭的就贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.71,0:01:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集群防禦系統啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.55,0:01:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一、第二靈智型部隊在西南方島嶼迎擊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.32,0:01:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三、第四、第五部隊在本島西南沿岸佈下防線
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.49,0:02:01.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓那些來自宇宙的鼠輩見識一下人類的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.43,0:02:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以見識到人類軍的本事了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.20,0:02:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是他們連所羅門系統都還不會使用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.87,0:02:12.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旺茲是位優秀的指揮官
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.17,0:02:13.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該不會這麼輕易敗北
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.37,0:02:17.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會祈禱他們不要重蹈摩達維亞的覆轍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.94,0:02:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弓子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.21,0:02:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在CDC是人類軍的指揮總部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.18,0:02:23.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳去那裡又能做什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.58,0:02:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連系統都不會用的人 我怎麼能信賴他們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.15,0:02:29.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 你要做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.56,0:02:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想以這種方式跟妳重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.86,0:02:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛耶 你要做什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.30,0:02:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.80,0:02:42.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳先待在裡面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.30,0:02:50.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳能夠活在世界上的某處 就是我唯一上戰場的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.81,0:02:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弓子…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.85,0:02:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.02,0:03:02.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為我走太慢才害妳跟不上大家的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.89,0:03:05.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係啦 不過妳不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.52,0:03:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我才剛到外面來而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.76,0:03:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不太適應怎麼走路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.63,0:03:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就邊休息邊走吧 不要太勉強了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.20,0:03:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳願意聽我一個請求嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.37,0:03:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 要我揹妳都沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.94,0:03:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.31,0:03:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望妳可以當我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.84,0:03:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我連一個朋友都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.81,0:03:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.58,0:03:33.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳的朋友不就在這裡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.72,0:03:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳 小芹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.56,0:03:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用客氣…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.53,0:03:42.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有自我介紹過嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.23,0:03:44.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.93,0:03:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是避難所的入口
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.50,0:03:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快進去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.10,0:03:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.77,0:03:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小芹就跟大家在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.34,0:03:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.91,0:04:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字叫做乙姬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.08,0:04:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆城乙姬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.78,0:04:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆城不就是總士學長的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.42,0:04:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說定囉 我們要當朋友喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.36,0:04:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友 - 歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.80,0:04:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一波動屏障被消滅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.54,0:04:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人沒有變更前進路線 正筆直往這裡前進
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.31,0:04:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直線前進嗎 竟敢瞧不起我們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.81,0:04:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 已經取得外出許可了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.75,0:04:38.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這個意思 我是為了比較虛弱的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.02,0:04:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種時候人類彼此卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.69,0:04:49.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.83,0:04:51.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鶴 妳在那裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.96,0:04:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有事情要麻煩當初把我放到系統裡面的妳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.83,0:04:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳…難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.14,0:05:02.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出生至今第一次來到外界 所以我還不太會走路
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.48,0:05:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請妳拿一個可以載我移動的東西過來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.92,0:05:13.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二波動屏障被突破了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.15,0:05:13.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.49,0:05:20.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校也卯足全力了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.73,0:05:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說對吧 卡農
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.29,0:05:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也比平常還有精神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.50,0:05:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛剛去見我以前的女人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.30,0:05:29.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.73,0:05:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神劍型法夫那要出馬囉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.18,0:05:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在西南方登陸 自爆了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.82,0:05:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是昂宿型的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.76,0:05:53.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Triple SIX 前往支援！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.69,0:05:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就到囉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.97,0:06:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡農 帶第三部隊繞到左邊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.97,0:06:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要夾擊它們了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.04,0:06:05.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.14,0:06:08.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險 在搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.21,0:06:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 連無線通訊都沒有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.91,0:06:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 Mark III！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.15,0:06:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.05,0:06:18.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.62,0:06:25.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機體表面跟皮膚的觸感同步的程度居然這麼高
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.16,0:06:28.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體好沈重
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.16,0:06:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是神劍型的特徵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.29,0:06:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快和它同化並接受變性意識
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.23,0:06:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.87,0:06:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帳 站起來打 不然會沒命的！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.01,0:06:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆城…乙姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.51,0:06:50.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次這樣跟妳說話呢 千鶴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.89,0:07:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨蛇級潛水艦被擊中 三艘都被擊沈了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.33,0:07:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人的首領呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.69,0:07:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒找到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.33,0:07:05.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通知另外的兩艘潛水艇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.96,0:07:08.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對西南部沿岸進行密集攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.72,0:07:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連自己人也一起打？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.69,0:07:35.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙姬！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.00,0:07:42.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有生以來第一次玩泥巴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.94,0:07:48.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.64,0:07:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心 只是表面燒掉而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.64,0:07:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要選擇是從現在才開始喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.71,0:07:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西方出現了第三群
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.75,0:07:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.15,0:08:03.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這座島的西南部份切離 用系統讓它自爆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.32,0:08:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把登陸的敵人和島嶼一起炸掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.66,0:08:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎擊系統自行運作 拒絕我們的手動控制了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.29,0:08:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.23,0:08:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會動？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.43,0:08:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰在操縱的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.84,0:08:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法查明
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.74,0:08:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,門打開了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.74,0:08:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吃飯了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.08,0:08:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是什麼狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.11,0:08:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總部、總部
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.62,0:08:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 接不通
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.98,0:08:36.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指揮系統似乎被截斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.75,0:08:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情勢正有所變化
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.76,0:08:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉讓我們離開這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.36,0:08:43.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道生？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.64,0:08:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？這是誰幹的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.42,0:09:09.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劍司
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.89,0:09:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.26,0:09:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次是那一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.16,0:09:21.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來好像是想要引導我們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.01,0:09:32.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是妳嗎 乙姬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.41,0:09:36.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重新建立防線
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.28,0:09:37.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還能動的傢伙通通到前面！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.46,0:09:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大量的昂宿型異界體在龍宮山頂集結
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.39,0:09:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在我們正上方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.53,0:09:50.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.97,0:09:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙姬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.47,0:10:00.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.97,0:10:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是島的痛楚傳到我身上而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.91,0:10:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是停手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.21,0:10:07.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬一妳有什麼三長兩短…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.44,0:10:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我躲起來的話 這座島一定會沉沒的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.22,0:10:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這之前 我必須讓大家做出選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.93,0:10:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍骨區塊 (Keel Block)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.96,0:10:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是兀爾德之泉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.11,0:10:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是強迫要接受的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.98,0:10:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要以自己的意志重新選擇嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.89,0:10:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.49,0:10:55.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.49,0:10:59.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別發呆了 快上去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.66,0:11:00.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要駕駛嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.03,0:11:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不穿作用服？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.90,0:11:05.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一騎也曾經沒換裝就駕駛吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.47,0:11:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何況…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.17,0:11:11.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果現在不戰鬥就對不起我爸跟甲洋他們了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.68,0:11:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的工作是給予大家想要得到的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.42,0:11:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓大家再做一次選擇 確定所要的究竟是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.32,0:11:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而這對異界體也是相同的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.82,0:11:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要請它們做選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.99,0:11:31.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此我才會誕生的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.20,0:11:34.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.93,0:11:39.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鶴回去吧 避難所還很安全
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.44,0:11:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳陪我來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.94,0:11:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鶴？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.81,0:11:50.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.45,0:11:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為系統的研究員
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.35,0:11:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 身為島上的居民我要親眼見證一切
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.69,0:12:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弓子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.03,0:12:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳也來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.09,0:12:03.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.23,0:12:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是被引導來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.56,0:12:07.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡到底是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.84,0:12:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所羅門的本體
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.97,0:12:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.21,0:12:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟王之室
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.44,0:12:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是第二CDC嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.81,0:12:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人各就各位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.35,0:12:26.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本構造跟CDC一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.35,0:12:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認所有系統
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.89,0:12:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把龍宮島的主控權拿回來！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.10,0:12:48.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是這座島 這座島就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.87,0:12:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在島上的人們想將島變成什麼樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.38,0:12:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那些人們的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.88,0:12:59.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們實際上在追求什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.52,0:13:02.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓人們得以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.42,0:13:07.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能做的只有請他們做出選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.53,0:13:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓人們得以理解…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.80,0:13:15.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當初我沒能讓妳做出選擇…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.17,0:13:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我也選擇過囉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.27,0:13:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁有自我 這就是我的選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.41,0:13:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就在這裡喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.25,0:13:35.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前有117隻登陸 敵方勢力更加擴大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.89,0:13:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昂宿型會發現這裡只是時間上的問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.66,0:13:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二防衛系統呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.26,0:13:42.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在執行中 再兩分鐘完成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.96,0:13:45.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,群體中誕生的主體將索敵系統無效化
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.03,0:13:47.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法發現本體！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.56,0:13:50.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以拿法夫那當誘餌 引誘出敵人的首領嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.67,0:13:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很難 但我試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.67,0:13:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌聲？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.31,0:13:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.23,0:14:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所羅門有反應了 是敵人首領
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.73,0:14:21.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將所有迎擊系統集中起來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.00,0:14:23.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌聲的來源在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.33,0:14:25.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是龍宮島西邊的燈塔 我把影像顯示在螢幕上面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.10,0:14:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.57,0:14:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆城乙姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.61,0:14:34.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳也要讓異界體選擇嗎 乙姬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.48,0:14:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人本體開始朝燈塔移動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.61,0:14:40.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有法夫那散開 立刻往島的西邊移動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.85,0:14:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,避開敵人前往指示的地點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.85,0:14:45.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要攻擊敵人的本體！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.69,0:14:46.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.86,0:14:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是什麼敵人我都會打倒的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.09,0:14:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕、好可怕喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.33,0:14:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衝吧 高拜！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.34,0:15:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.61,0:15:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的動作…是駕駛員換人了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.04,0:15:07.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡農 找到敵方首領了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.84,0:15:08.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們往西邊移動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.98,0:15:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.15,0:15:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他還可以動的也跟著我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.15,0:15:13.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.02,0:15:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海底飛彈準備完成
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.15,0:15:17.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部發射！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.67,0:15:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.40,0:15:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.37,0:15:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mark V以神盾系統阻止敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.91,0:15:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mark VIII繞到右側
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.94,0:15:39.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mark III確認敵方核心並且將其破壞！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.69,0:15:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃啊 劍司！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.26,0:15:58.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劍司！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.40,0:15:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准去 維持陣型！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.76,0:16:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢如此！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.92,0:16:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來不及了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.45,0:16:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連神劍型也抵擋不了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.32,0:16:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在上面！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.06,0:16:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帳東西！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.96,0:16:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個怪物！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.33,0:16:34.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太強了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.50,0:16:37.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標再度朝燈塔移動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.57,0:16:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆城乙姬呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.57,0:16:39.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並沒有移動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.59,0:16:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 你們也選好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.36,0:16:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有對話的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.53,0:16:54.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都會消失的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.17,0:16:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虛無的道路…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.61,0:17:04.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.35,0:17:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做選擇的並不是只有你們喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.02,0:17:10.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.22,0:17:13.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙姬 我們逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.46,0:17:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鶴 謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.63,0:17:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.80,0:17:25.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.64,0:17:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼機體？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.89,0:17:47.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擋下來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.43,0:17:56.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是剛才的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.50,0:18:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 會被炸掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.67,0:18:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人的核心正從內部被消滅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.35,0:18:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道異界體…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.51,0:18:16.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反倒被同化了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.32,0:18:22.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標又開始消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.46,0:18:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.29,0:18:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所羅門的反應消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.09,0:18:27.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要尋找就找得到喔 總士
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.06,0:18:28.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙姬！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.46,0:18:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振動、各種波形、溫度、電子、電波、空間相位
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.97,0:18:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.37,0:18:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架機體攻擊之後所留下來的傷痕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.84,0:18:40.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛員 你聽得到嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.84,0:18:43.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人的位置捕捉到了 幫忙打倒那傢伙吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.75,0:18:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總士
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.32,0:18:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一…騎…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.15,0:18:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要跟系統同步
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.36,0:18:57.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該能跟Mark XI那時候一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.86,0:19:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今你還在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.07,0:19:12.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總士 你曾經說過只有這座島是唯一的樂園
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.41,0:19:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當初我不懂這句話的含意 也不知道你在想些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.61,0:19:19.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是聽你的話去戰鬥而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.55,0:19:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過現在我覺得有點懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.86,0:19:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你懂了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.59,0:19:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實你一直很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.53,0:19:43.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從我們一無所知的時候 你就想要保護這座島
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.60,0:19:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是翔子還有甲洋那時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.57,0:19:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也獨自背負著痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.84,0:19:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你絕對…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.68,0:19:58.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架機體的識別代號是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.89,0:20:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mark Zein
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.52,0:20:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要跟系統同步必須登錄機體
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.06,0:20:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我五秒鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.13,0:20:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總士？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.30,0:20:09.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.80,0:20:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,登錄完畢 開始同步處理
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.71,0:20:24.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.15,0:20:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得見我看到的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.11,0:20:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看得到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.05,0:20:29.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.23,0:20:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個武器是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.43,0:20:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是Mark VIII的44機關砲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.47,0:20:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可怕的威力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.47,0:20:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路迦之槍嗎！
